<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-70-1234 </DOCNO><TEXT>The patent relates to electron and x-ray detector systems used with electronmicroscopes, and describes a protection system to limit excessive radiationat the detector. The semiconductor detector is mounted at the end ofa probe, and a shutter is located at the detector end of the probe. Theshutter is open in normal use. However if the current in the detectorexceeds a threshold value then the shutter is closed either manuallyor automatically. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>